toBeEqual

public JodaTimePreconditions toBeEqual(org.joda.time.base.BaseLocal expectedValue,
                                       String expectedLabel)
Ensures given base local is equal to expected value. Override default implementation and uses isEquals() because Joda Time's equals() takes account of chronology, which is too strict.
